<item>
 <title>4.12 Release Time</title>
 <link>https://www.middlebury.edu/old-about/old-handbook/handbook_archive/handbook-2018-2019/ug-college-policies/employee/time_away/release_time/node/632238</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Release time may be approved by the president or her designee, in order to allow staff to attend certain campus-wide events. If release time falls during an employee&#039;s regularly scheduled hours it is considered regular paid time. If release time falls during a time when an employee is not scheduled to work, he or she may choose to attend the event, but the time is unpaid.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
